# PHP standards

See **[AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)** ("Standards"). In short: PHP 8.5+, `declare(strict_types=1);` in every file, PSR-12, short array syntax. Namespaces — app code `OpenEHR\BmmPublisher\*`, console commands `OpenEHR\BmmPublisher\Console\Command\*`, tests `Tests\*`.

Run `php` / `composer` / PHPUnit **inside the dev container** only (`make ci`, `make sh`).
